# Subagents

Subagents are defined in `.cursor/subagents/`. The `.cursor/agents` symlink points to `subagents/` so Cursor loads them from that directory.

To set up or reset this configuration, run:
```bash
./scripts/setup-subagents.sh
```

Use `/subagent-setup` or invoke the subagent-setup subagent to run the migration.
